### List all resturant with a limit of 10
GET http://localhost:8000/api/resturant?limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

### Get a resturant by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/resturant/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Create a new resturant
POST http://localhost:8000/api/resturant
Content-Type: application/json

{
   "name":"Riyan dines",
   "street_address":"40076",
