}


### Update a resturant by ID
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/resturant/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
   "name":"Soohyun diner"
}

### Delete a resturant by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/resturant/1
Content-Type: application/json
